      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.XrBOn1MueVB4u5sV]{Nanocyte Knack}</p>\n<p>You can use your nanites on mechs you pilot, making them an extension of your own body. You can apply the effects of your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.QoCQEVNtgMhsElwQ]{Sheath Array (Ex)} to any mechs that you are piloting. Once per combat, you can spend a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.vh6n0Ad3lamOJXpV]{Nanite Surge (Ex)} to give the mech a number of temporary Hit Points equal to your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.classes.Item.MMyeA7kL5Vhcio05]{Nanocyte} level; the mech loses any such remaining temporary Hit Points when the sheath array ends.</p>"
